D64::Disk::Layout Version 0.01
==============================

D64::Disk::Layout provides a low-level helper class for D64::Disk module,
enabling users to directly access and manipulate entire D64/D71/D81 disk
image data in an object oriented way without the hassle of worrying about
the meaning of individual bits and bytes located on every track and sector
of a physical disk image.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

